{"tid":2263904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國16歲偶像小男星陷色情短訊醜聞 勾引女網友「睡覺」：弟弟受不了！","createTime":"2020-10-30T08:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T20:19:51.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"7860bfb15ac1c7aa471f9b7e2809267d39ad5e54","tid":2263904,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf091ab0250a8c5b78408b834897cd7eaa65ab2","tid":2263904,"uid":256783,"like":236,"dislike":0,"score":236,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"畀十秒你"},{"pid":"382b24c9c9b6388b762dc7e0582a3f57bf28c105","tid":2263904,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":128,"score":-122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"近期中國不斷培訓自家本土偶像明星，但最近傳出一名年約16歲的小男星張銘浩，小小年紀就懂得寫出鹹濕簡訊，甚至要約「姐姐」開房，其尺度大到跌破許多人的眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n事件起因於一名中國微博網友在本月27日爆料，稱自己的姊妹和一名16歲小鮮肉戀愛，但感到對方無緣無故變得冷淡，於是決定曝光兩人的簡訊內容，算是一種「報復」。<br />\n<br />\n該名網友曝光的簡訊內容包括：「弟弟受不了了了。」、「想跟姐姐睡覺。」、「等你回來，老公X死你。」、「我們去民宿，做完我就給你送回去。」以上簡訊內容，全部出自16歲小鮮肉之手，曝光後讓許多網友感到震驚，認為這名小鮮肉小小年紀，但早已懂得使用淫穢不堪的詞彙，連成人看了都臉紅心跳。<br />\n<br />\n事後有網友進一步比對，認為網友口中的這名「小鮮肉」，應該就是「YHBOYS」的成員張銘浩。網友還爆料稱，這名小男星剛認識「姐姐」不久後，就有意開房，並且三番五次找「姐姐」給他買手機、買東西或轉帳。但小男星達到目的之後，就開始對「姐姐」變得冷淡，「姐姐」不甘被當工具人，於是透過朋友進行網路爆料...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201030/SKGGAAZWRNHEFILG27ZLLSKYPM/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2LVjPW4hZ1XOZ3l4OtRiBUJeuUu5hAQzLl-VvtBRYBgwWTxYQS3l2gfgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201030%2FSKGGAAZWRNHEFILG27ZLLSKYPM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2LVjPW4hZ1XOZ3l4OtRiBUJeuUu5hAQzLl-VvtBRYBgwWTxYQS3l2gfgQ&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=14b5d27e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201030%2FSKGGAAZWRNHEFILG27ZLLSKYPM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2LVjPW4hZ1XOZ3l4OtRiBUJeuUu5hAQzLl-VvtBRYBgwWTxYQS3l2gfgQ&h=fdeab726\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201030/SKGGAAZWRNHEFILG27ZLLSKYPM/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2LVjPW4hZ1XOZ3l4OtRiBUJeuUu5hAQzLl-VvtBRYBgwWTxYQS3l2gfgQ</a>"},{"pid":"e6307cc0369b507033853f85bab39edabc563920","tid":2263904,"uid":93212,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a335146af5e567294430d5ed4baa8ec8b7ea09","tid":2263904,"uid":63113,"like":251,"dislike":8,"score":243,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9D4eh0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9D4eh0q.png&h=eac0de56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vAUh0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vAUh0s.png&h=90d86937&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ny6TyO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ny6TyO.gif&h=fe1355bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d878490c129aef674f4d65045ceaaa1706d748e8","tid":2263904,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:33:33.000Z","msg":"弟弟不行了"},{"pid":"9dbd402f068534f4ebfc5d039751bde49c772803","tid":2263904,"uid":176313,"like":313,"dislike":1,"score":312,"quote":{"pid":"13a335146af5e567294430d5ed4baa8ec8b7ea09","tid":2263904,"uid":63113,"like":251,"dislike":8,"score":243,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9D4eh0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt